{"tid":670655,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"所謂輪迴會唔會係不停輪迴同一世？","createTime":"2018-05-19T14:24:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-19T17:35:31.000Z","uid":121336,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fc7458a0824928a95deaf3550e7c33ecbc212956","tid":670655,"uid":121336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T14:24:20.000Z","msg":"最近突然產生種念頭，<br />\n所謂輪迴好多人會覺得係投胎做第二個人，<br />\n但係再幻想下，<br />\n如果所謂輪迴係輪迴返同一世做返同一個人呢？<br />\n<br />\n譬如今世如果我死前覺得自己一世人做錯太多決定，<br />\n我就會再重新輪迴一次無限 loop，<br />\n唔知點解我覺得呢種想法好可怕，<br />\n好多人覺得死係解脫，<br />\n但萬一死唔係解脫呢？<br />\n好似生生世世都被trap住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f76623b240bdba53e11886f1d8f952d1c6222dfc","tid":670655,"uid":74262,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T14:25:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e8987f5458849325a94004082070c113eb564a74","tid":670655,"uid":12618,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T14:26:30.000Z","msg":"下世做樹都唔掂"},{"pid":"588c5c2efc3aedd89c01cab7c738b67054358562","tid":670655,"uid":121336,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f76623b240bdba53e11886f1d8f952d1c6222dfc","tid":670655,"uid":74262,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T14:25:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T14:30:57.000Z","msg":"死後會發生咩事無人知，<br />\n但係我總係覺得人死如燈滅呢個說法太膚淺，<br />\n<br />\n如果死左真係咩都無，<br />\n姐係所有afterlife theory，宗教，鬼怪之類都係9up？"},{"pid":"67021f717bdbc1e2d69476b7977c1ca2af212c61","tid":670655,"uid":30186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T14:32:19.000Z","msg":"點為之同一個人"},{"pid":"70f7d31bac02e29a8179144246e8357432f2d1d4","tid":670655,"uid":121336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e8987f5458849325a94004082070c113eb564a74","tid":670655,"uid":12618,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T14:26:30.000Z","msg":"下世做樹都唔掂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T14:33:38.000Z","msg":"做樹就好似被上天罰要靜思己過"}